{"tid":1529150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日見到香港人幾團結","createTime":"2019-09-01T16:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-12T05:38:24.000Z","uid":276319,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"461ced702298a0005b392e09aa047d125c2034da","tid":1529150,"uid":276319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:22:09.000Z","msg":"發夢去左東涌先一齊入左地鐵站參觀大堂 控制室 之後路障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後5點幾有人話啲狗黎緊 好多手足男女老幼都即刻跑走 有啲跑去東薈城 有啲跑去逸東 有啲跑去迎東 有啲跑去碼頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 而碼頭有船去屯門愉景灣個啲 但原來屯門船得番2班 每架船得百幾個位 但成堆人走難（可能都有一萬人）點走得切 於是有啲人排船 有啲人排巴士 排排下居然見到有架本身唔係碼頭有站嘅巴士突然出現 載左好多人 然後因爲個刻又大風又落雨 又排隊 有啲人選擇行去北大嶼山公路 有啲人排巴士 有啲人等朋友義載<br />\n去到6點半個陣有手足講船得番440個位 但係就一定載唔到全部人 好多人比晒有需要人上船先 怕佢地番唔到屋企 尤其比左中學生先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後去到7點開始有番e車出現 仲車左好多人走 有一架e車多人到上層走廊位坐滿人 仲3個人坐2個位 司機話目的要比大部分係碼頭等車乘客上到晒 最後架車梗係滿晒人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後7點3上車 沿路不斷塞 好多人怕大家肚餓分野食 希望大家可以頂到落車 去到十點個陣成車人一齊嗌光復香港時代革命好撚壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲嗌左幾分鐘 到左11點終於見到青馬收費廣場 成車人歡呼 大叫離開欣澳 可以返屋企 成車人幾開心 最後每個站落車 都同司機講句多謝 又大嗌光復香港時代革命 司機答番大家香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日發夢長征4小時由東涌去青馬收費廣場發現香港人仲係好團結 唔會怕左呢個垃圾政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成車人不斷講唔好搭黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18607d4d02f61c10ec9166885fba88e535e0a2a5","tid":1529150,"uid":79704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16d575c88fbd8a2f1f7d487d34470f115e93eba9","tid":1529150,"uid":83250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57cf01ffcb117a7315db0b21e002ea484d9f7964","tid":1529150,"uid":263367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:24:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d660478ca6d9b6d02d109c08e8e4709061169215","tid":1529150,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6da3eaca007a704dd0db4fb39686bedae0c88b8","tid":1529150,"uid":68146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:52:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3787d6450ae9efa0379f93d402e3b1b1b64d2df","tid":1529150,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/01/223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F01%2F223606_db1fcc72048388792c25c8bdc081a00b.gif&h=16fdca9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民學唱<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span><br />\n<br />\n<em>&quot;The Star-Spangled Banner&quot;</em><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as